name: Rebase
description: Force a context rebase — write state to files and prepare for a clean session

---
Perform a context rebase.

1. Write the current project state to protocol/state.md — phase, last completed stage, active jobs, open items
2. Write any incomplete or deferred work to tasks/workboard.md
3. Produce a compact 3-5 bullet summary of what happened this session

Then confirm the rebase is complete and ask the user whether to continue in this session or start fresh.
